            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. STO staggers delivery over 24-48 hours, which means some subscribers may not receive your email until the next day. For flash sales, event reminders, breaking news, or time-sensitive promotions, a fixed immediate send time is the right approach. Reserve STO for newsletters, nurture sequences, and evergreen campaigns.</p></div></div>
